## {% worker name="archer" /%} in Training
{% worker name="archer" plural=true /%} in Training will train at the {% building name="archery" /%} to become an {% worker name="archer" /%}. They will use a bow to shoot practice dummies and will level up without a risk of dying to mobs.

{% worker name="archer" plural=true /%} in Training are not actual guards even though they are dressed in the usual guard clothes. They will not help defend your colony, only guards will do that.
